description:
I'm an open source nhentai Discord bot powered by [TypeScript](https://www.typescriptlang.org/) with [discord.js](https://discord.js.org/#/) using the [Akairo](https://discord-akairo.github.io/#/) framework.

About the name:
**Inari Ōkami** (Japanese: 稲荷大神), also called Ō-Inari (大稲荷), is the Japanese kami of foxes, of **fertility**, rice, tea and sake, of agriculture and industry, of general prosperity and worldly success, and one of the principal kami of Shinto.
